INSTALLATION:
=============

Before attempting to install SkOP on your computer, you have to make
sure that the following depencies are available:

Dependencies:
-------------
- Qt4 <http://www.qtsoftware.com/	downloads>
- cfitsio <http://heasarc.gsfc.nasa.gov/fitsio>
- GLEW <http://glew.sourceforge.net>
- An OpenGL implementation

The build operation also requires the cmake utility
<http://www.cmake.org>. Then type:

cmake .
make

and optionnally:

make install
